---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="Organizing tests — MCP Studio" current="organizing">

  <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--muted-foreground)] mb-4">
    [ Organizing tests ]
  </p>
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-4">Tags and running tests</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted-foreground)] max-w-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
    [Intro: once you have more than a few tests, tags keep things navigable. Run all tests at once or filter by tag.]
  </p>

  <!-- Tags -->
  <section id="tags" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-1">Tags</h2>
    <p class="text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-lg">
      [How tags are added when saving a test. How to filter by tag in the Tests drawer. Tags are lowercase and deduplicated.]
    </p>
    <div class="border border-dashed border-[var(--border)] h-40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
      screenshot: tests drawer with tag filter
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Run all -->
  <section id="run-all" class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--foreground)] mb-1">Run all</h2>
    <p class="text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-lg">
      [How to run all tests or all tests matching a tag. What the run group view shows: passed, failed, duration per test. Where to find history of past runs.]
    </p>
    <div class="border border-dashed border-[var(--border)] h-40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-[var(--muted-foreground)]">
      screenshot: run group result summary
    </div>
  </section>

</DocsLayout>
